<%- include('layouts/header') -%>
  <h2 style="color: #202742;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: normal;">
    Hi <%= name %>,
  </h2>
  <h1 style="color: #202742;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: normal;">
    Reset your password
  </h1>
  <p style="color: #4F4F4F;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 26px;
      text-align: left;">
    We have received a request to reset the password for your PROJECT account. To proceed with the password reset
    process, please follow the instructions below:
  </p>
  <ol>
    <li style="color: #4F4F4F;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 26px;
      text-align: left;">
      Click on the following link to reset your password:
    </li>
    <a href="<%=url %>" target="_blank">
      <button type="button" style="color: #FFF;
      font-feature-settings: 'ss11' on, 'cv09' on, 'liga' off, 'calt' off;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -0.084px;
      margin: 16px 0;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      background: #FE9D04;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      cursor: pointer;">
        Reset Password
      </button>
    </a>
    <li style="color: #4F4F4F;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 26px;
      text-align: left;">
      Once you've clicked the link or entered the URL, you will be directed to a page where you can set a new password
      for your PROJECT account.
    </li>
  </ol>

  <p style="color: #4F4F4F;
      font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-style: normal;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 26px;
      text-align: left;">
    Please note that this link is time-sensitive and will expire after a certain period for security purposes. If you
    did not request this password reset, please ignore this email.
  </p>

  <%- include('layouts/footer') -%>